sets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呀邊個邊個 你記唔記得你中學果陣掉左我個書包落垃圾桶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8000c265c75f4382f2b5737aa6604af3e348cb9","tid":732104,"uid":146924,"like":246,"dislike":0,"score":246,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T21:26:32.000Z","msg":"難咩受吖 大把人當初差過你而家都喺你之上<br />\n最緊要係你同人之前冇結過怨<br />\n仲好添啦你朝中有人好辦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2d3a1c8b3cf8409eb8d86aebd85bad596a927e","tid":732104,"uid":642,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T23:57:33.000Z","msg":"重點係你以前有冇得罪過佢啫"},{"pid":"17ec222ebbc91e433a4f1f533d74a1ed21ecc78b","tid":732104,"uid":190358,"like":1,"dislike":56,"score":-55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:37:05.000Z","msg":"唔喜歡, 可搵個份. <br />\n我慘過你, 以前同學, 高我六級"},{"pid":"95f885f51b0f1388f5ae40ff69c45adc6b24ca19","tid":732104,"uid":145307,"like":12,"dislike":29,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"上個月幫老闆interview見番個小學男同學 記得佢細個讀書好叻又拎科目獎又做咩班長嗰d 不過大大下唔知咩原因就變得普普通通，好多年冇見不過有對方Facebook. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後老闆請左第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374a01ba5f90677d68d1701a700b4b155f162515","tid":732104,"uid":119330,"like":120,"dislike":1,"score":119,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"讀書同做野係兩回事<br />\n分數並不能反映所有<br />\n<br />\nBtw 舊同學有呢個機會<br />\n咪係過塘養肥自己<br />\n你敢唔敢行呢一步"},{"pid":"f42f665128c3d2894ff6570391f86ce1445f9ea9","tid":732104,"uid":59828,"like":47,"dislike":9,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"有個中學同學而家揸住幾層樓，自己做老細，搞緊移民日本<br />\n